headline: Macao Enterprises Take Trip to Lisbon with Sands China
summary: A delegation of 17 Macao enterprises took a trip to Lisbon on Sands China's invitation to participate in the company's five-day Macao Technological Innovation Exploration in Lisbon Nov. 11-15. The trip aimed to foster the long-term development of technological innovation in Macao, in alignment with Macao SAR government's vision.
